# ============================================================================
# Google Gemini API Key Pool - 20-Key Rotation System
# ============================================================================
#
# SCALING STRATEGY:
# - 20 API keys in round-robin rotation
# - Each user starts at random position (0-19) on first launch
# - Then follows deterministic sequence forever
# - Perfect even distribution: each key gets 1/20th of total requests
# - Handles 10,000+ concurrent users without rate limit issues
#
# QUOTA CAPACITY:
# - Each key: 60 req/min, 1,500 req/day, 2.5M req/month
# - 20 keys total: 1,200 req/min, 30,000 req/day, 50M req/month
# - Supports ~350,000 active users (5 messages/day avg)
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Create 20 API keys in Google Cloud Console: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Apply bundle ID restrictions to EACH key (com.everydaychristian.app)
# 3. Set API restrictions: Generative Language API only
# 4. Set billing alerts: $50 warning, $100 cap per key
# 5. Replace placeholders below with actual keys
# 6. Keep GEMINI_API_KEY as fallback (backward compatibility)
#
# ============================================================================

